## 🛠️ **EXECUTION ENVIRONMENT SETUP**

### Prerequisites Validation
```bash
# Verify all prerequisites are met
devenv shell                                    # Enter NixOS environment
podman --version                               # Verify Podman 5.4.1+
pg_isready -h localhost -p 5433 -U postgres   # Verify PostgreSQL 17
redis-cli -h localhost -p 6379 ping           # Verify Redis 7
```

### Environment Configuration
```bash
# Set required environment variables
export PHICS_ENABLED=true
export ELIXIR_ERL_OPTIONS="+S 16"
export CONTAINER_ENFORCEMENT=true

# Create PHICS marker file
touch .phics

# Validate PHICS integration
elixir scripts/pcis/validation_cli.exs --phics-compliance
```

### Database Preparation
```bash
# Ensure database is ready for demos
mix ecto.create     # Create database if needed
mix ecto.migrate    # Apply all migrations
mix ecto.reset      # Reset if clean state needed
```

