## 🚨 **TROUBLESHOOTING & DIAGNOSTICS**

### System Health Validation
```bash
# Comprehensive system diagnostics
elixir scripts/demo/demo_health_validator.exs --comprehensive

# Container status validation
elixir scripts/performance/podman_direct_manager.exx --status

# PHICS compliance verification
elixir scripts/pcis/validation_cli.exs --all
```

### Common Issues & Solutions

#### Container Connection Issues
```bash
# Check container status
podman ps | grep intelitor

# Restart containers if needed
podman restart intelitor-postgres-demo intelitor-redis-demo intelitor-app-demo

# Verify network connectivity
podman network ls | grep intelitor-demo
```

#### Database Issues
```bash
# Check PostgreSQL connectivity
pg_isready -h localhost -p 5433 -U postgres

# Reset database if needed
mix ecto.reset
```

#### Performance Issues
```bash
# Monitor system resources
elixir scripts/performance/comprehensive_performance_test.exs --export

# Check compilation performance
time elixir -e "Code.eval_file(\"scripts/demo/simple_container_validation.exs\")"
```

